Title: Software Bug Report
Description: I encountered a critical bug in the latest software update. Whenever I try to open the application, it crashes immediately. This issue is preventing me from completing my work. Urgent attention is needed.

Title: Hardware Malfunction
Description: My laptop's keyboard is malfunctioning. Some keys are unresponsive, and it's affecting my productivity. I've tried cleaning it, but the problem persists. I need assistance to fix this issue as soon as possible.

Title: New Feature Request
Description: I have a suggestion for a new feature in our app. It would be great to have a dark mode option for night-time usage. This feature can improve user experience. I would like to discuss this idea further with the development team.

Title: Network Connectivity Issue
Description: Our office is experiencing network connectivity problems. Internet access is slow, and employees are unable to access critical online resources. We need immediate troubleshooting and resolution to ensure uninterrupted workflow.

Title: Website Redesign Request
Description: We're looking to give our website a fresh new look to improve user engagement and navigation. The current design feels outdated, and we believe a redesign will enhance our online presence. We're seeking proposals from web designers and developers.

Title: Data Backup Request
Description: We need to schedule regular data backups for our company's server. It's crucial to ensure data safety and disaster recovery. We're looking for a solution that automates this process and keeps our data secure.

Title: Security Vulnerability Report
Description: We've identified a potential security vulnerability in our web application. It could lead to unauthorized access and data breaches. We urgently need a security audit and fix to protect our user's information.

Title: Employee Training Request
Description: We want to organize a training session for our employees to enhance their skills in digital marketing. The training should cover social media marketing, SEO, and content creation. Looking for training providers and a suitable schedule.

Title: Product Enhancement Request
Description: We have feedback from customers about improving our product. The enhancements include adding new features and streamlining the user interface. This can make our product more competitive in the market.

Title: Expense Report Submission Issue
Description: I'm having trouble submitting my expense report through the online system. It's essential to get this resolved as it affects reimbursement for business expenses. I need assistance to ensure my report goes through successfully.
